    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been loved and well-cared for? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's honestly in great shape! It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Whether you're just commuting to work or planning a fun weekend road trip, this beauty won't let you down. It's super clean and drives so smoothly\u2014you've really gotta come take it for a spin to see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example benefits from a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS system overhaul, ensuring the double-variable valve timing operates within factory parameters. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, complemented by a limited-slip differential that provides predictable lock-up under load. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery and sharp throttle response from the individual throttle bodies. This is a performance-oriented driver's car that prioritizes mechanical excellence and analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean interior. Mechanically sound. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
